+### ldflags
+
+GoReleaser already sets a `main.version` ldflag, so, in you `main.go` program,
+you can:
+
+```go
+package main
+
+var version = "master"
+
+func main() {
+  println(version)
+}
+```
+
+And this version will always be the tag name.
+
